==Useful Info==
'''Great orbs of eyes''' are annoying spellcasting monsters with high [[willpower]]. They can be found in the middle- to late-[[Dungeon]], [[the Slime Pits]], and [[the Vaults]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Most of the threat comes from its spells. Having high [[willpower]] prevents most spells from affecting you, making them little more than marginally dangerous melee enemies. But if you don't have high will, they are ''very'' scary threats - [[polymorph]] is often a dangerous effect.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], they had [[Paralyse]] and [[Drain Magic]] instead of [[Vitrify]] and [[Polymorph]]. Also, their HD was 1 lower. 
*Prior to [[0.17]], they could [[Teleport Other]].
